    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>旅程开始</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人或与朋友一起冒险，挖掘神秘洞穴，打造强力武器与护甲，在一个程序生成的沙盒世界中努力生存。探索多样化的生物群系、隐藏洞窟、遥远岛屿、异界维度，甚至是漂浮的地牢。建造基地并吸引 NPC 推动故事发展。揭开这片破碎而被腐化的土地背后的真相。你能在邪恶吞噬一切之前阻止它吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/8e6e4c523ce41155c8ec9a62becf342d.poster.avif?t=1770361642\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/8e6e4c523ce41155c8ec9a62becf342d.webm?t=1770361642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/8e6e4c523ce41155c8ec9a62becf342d.mp4?t=1770361642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的职业</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为你想成为的英雄。选择盗贼、战士、游侠、法师或召唤师，每个职业都拥有独特技能、专属护甲套装和不同的武器风格。掌握你的职业，解锁强大的能力，在深入世界危险的同时塑造你的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/9cf85a5aca445229b3b50acc72c93448.poster.avif?t=1770361642\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/9cf85a5aca445229b3b50acc72c93448.webm?t=1770361642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/9cf85a5aca445229b3b50acc72c93448.mp4?t=1770361642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>等待你的内容</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成的体素世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人合作模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有挑战性的首领战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 个独特职业</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有独特进程的生物群系</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基地建造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主线与支线任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的地表与地下环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农耕、坐骑与宠物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地牢与稀有战利品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/07c483f7e1ab66187d6f191f770e7e73.poster.avif?t=1770361642\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/07c483f7e1ab66187d6f191f770e7e73.webm?t=1770361642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/07c483f7e1ab66187d6f191f770e7e73.mp4?t=1770361642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>埃尔德伍兹的秘密</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在海难中漂流上岸，你在一座危机四伏的岛屿上醒来。奇怪的生物侵扰着当地居民的梦境，而不断扩散的腐化正威胁着吞噬一切。邪恶的源头来自地底深处……远超任何人敢于探索的范围。你是夺回这片土地的最后希望。揭开埋藏在岩石之下的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1856810/extras/28d9bc37f14a96143afc02f8271fcaba.avif?t=1770361642\" width=922 height=78 /></span></p></li></ul>",
